item.description: That's fantastic news Conor! I'm sure this took a fair bit of persuasion from your part so fair play. I'm sure it will be a great success for all involved. I'm probably not ready this year, but if they go again next year I hopefully will be! Ciara
item.content:encoded:
That’s fantastic news Conor! I’m sure this took a fair bit of persuasion from your part so fair play. I’m sure it will be a great success for all involved. I’m probably not ready this year, but if they go again next year I hopefully will be!
Ciara
